Question mark. Yeah, so the quick answer is absolutely.

00:14:18.059 --> 00:14:19.619
We have a treasure trove of data.

00:14:19.619 --> 00:14:26.700
In fact, sometimes it feels a little bit like there's too much information and it kind of becomes

00:14:27.859 --> 00:14:32.539
more of a question of what is actually interesting rather than, you know, can we look at

00:14:32.539 --> 00:14:41.260
everything? The longer answer is that we have a bit of a odd company set up in that we are

