And should I ever start this, I have to pitch this idea and get by and you know how that goes.

00:51:17.260 --> 00:51:18.699
Maybe I'll report out someday.

00:51:20.459 --> 00:51:20.939
Thank you.

00:51:21.500 --> 00:51:23.020
It comes and goes in waves.

00:51:23.659 --> 00:51:26.699
So yeah, just keep with it.

00:51:26.699 --> 00:51:29.340
It's worth it once you get there.

