00:51:54.459 --> 00:51:59.419
at least in my part of the organization, got here through some internal mobility.

00:52:00.219 --> 00:52:04.300
We are the closet analysis analytics people.

00:52:04.300 --> 00:52:07.979
And I think that's probably true for a lot of us in this field.

